  p Bugmark is a market that connects people who want
    better software to people who can build it.
  p We make open collaboration more effecive, with
    simple market mechanisms that give users a way
    to hedge their exposure to software risk while
    giving developers incentives to increase software
    quality.

- content_for(:jumbo_hdr2) do
  | Bugmark enables you to

- content_for(:jumbo_body2) do
  ol
    li Put financial value directly in the hands of the people
       who can fix the software issues that are most important to
       you.
    li Discover which issues really matter to your project's users.
    li Work with open source practices and not against them.
