- content_for(:detail_hdr1) do
  | Find an issue, fix it and earn money

- content_for(:detail_body1) do
  | Visit Bugmark to find an open issue that matches your
    skills and interests.  Buy a futures contract connected to
    that issue that will pay you when the issue is fixed.  Work
    on the issue, in the open, then decide if you want to hold
    your contract until maturity, or sell it at a profit.

